'''[[颶風戈登_(1994年)|飓风戈登]]的气象历史'''持续了约13天的时间，这场风暴经久不散，行进路径飘忽不定且极不寻常。系统起初于1994年11月9日在[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西南部的[[巴拿马|巴拿马]]附近海域形成，以[[热带气旋|热带低气压]]强度掠过[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]并在该国近海徘徊了数天时间，然后系统略微增强成热带风暴并蜿蜒北上进入[[大安的列斯群岛|大安的列斯群岛]]海域，虽然途经洋面水温较高，但持续存在的[[风切变|风切变]]令其无法获得大幅增强。接下来戈登缓慢向北转向，之后又转朝西北进发，先后在[[牙买加|牙买加]]东部和[[古巴|古巴]]东部实现两次[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，同时还给[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]西部带去了倾盆大雨。

戈登以热带风暴强度在穿越[[佛罗里达礁岛群|佛罗里达礁岛群]]的过程中实现第四次登陆，并与[[对流层|上层对流层]]中的一个气旋以及一系列的气旋式[[低气压|低气压]]发生相互作用，令风暴拥有了部分[[副熱帶氣旋|亚热带特征]]。接下来几天时间里，位于[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]的系统很不寻常地拥有热带和亚热带天气系统的混合特征，然后再度恢复成热带风暴并又一次在[[佛罗里达半岛|佛罗里达半岛]]登陆。穿过该半岛后，系统进入[[大西洋|大西洋]]，并[[爆发性增强|爆发性增强]]成[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|一级飓风]]。戈登在漂移过程中曾短暂威胁到[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]，但之后又转向南下，减弱成一股强度较小的热带风暴并在佛罗里达州东海岸进行了第六次，也是最后一次登陆。

[[飓风戈登_(1994年)|飓风戈登]]是1994年大西洋飓风季获得命名的第七个风暴和第三场飓风。虽然每次登陆时都没有达到飓风强度，但其曲折的行进路径先后导致了六次登陆，其中四次有热带风暴强度，两次为热带低气压级别，有三次都是在[[美国|美国]]的[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达]][[美国州份|州]]。

== 形成 ==
1994年11月的第一个星期里，加勒比海西南部、巴拿马以北附近洋面累积形成了一片大范围的扰动气流。一股[[东风波|东风波]]穿过该区域，令气流中的[[对流|对流]]有所增加，11月6日，另一股东风波穿越这一海域，令扰动气流中开始具备[[热带气旋|气旋式环流]]。之后两天时间里，天气系统逐渐组织起来，并在尼加拉瓜东南近海爆发出深层对流<ref name="prelim">{{cite web | author = Pasch, Richard J. | publisher = National Hurricane Center | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Gordon 8–21 November 1994 | date = 1995-01-10 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | archivedate = 2013-09-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921205140/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1994gordon.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1994gordon.html }}</ref>。[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]将这片[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]达到每小时45公里的天气系统归类为第十二号热带低气压<ref name="TCD_01">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-08 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Depression Twelve Discussion Number 1 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.001 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021101752/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.001 }}</ref>。低气压在向西北方向前进的过程中缓慢增强<ref name="prelim" />，外界环境中的上层外流开始有利于其进一步发展<ref name="TCD_02">{{cite web | author = Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-08 | accessdate = 2008-07-14 | title = Tropical Depression Twelve Discussion Number 2 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.002 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021101829/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.002 }}</ref>。11月9日早上，对流开始出现爆发<ref name="TCD_03">{{cite web | author = Rappaport | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-09 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Depression Twelve Discussion Number 3 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.003 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021101835/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.003 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。风暴中心在接近[[卡贝萨斯港|卡贝萨斯港]]的尼加拉瓜东北海岸登陆时已经呈现出[[雨带|带状]]特征<ref name="TCD_05">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-09 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Depression Twelve Discussion Number 5 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.005 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021101844/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.005 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>。过了整整一天后，墨西哥湾上空，风暴西北方向的一个[[低压槽|低压槽]]令低气压向东北方向的海上进发<ref name="TCD_04">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-09 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Depression Twelve Discussion Number 4 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021101914/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.004 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.004 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>，并经过了加勒比海西部[[海面温度|海面温度]]较高的区域<ref name="prelim" />。由于有温暖的海水推波助澜，低气压于11月9日晚增强成热带风暴，风暴达到每小时65公里，美国国家飓风中心因此将其命名为“戈登”（{{lang|en|Gordon}}）<ref name="TCD_09">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-10 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 9 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102421/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.008 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.008 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>。

由于转向气流力道不强，风暴的行进方向很不稳定<ref name="TCD_09" />。戈登因少量西南偏西方向风切变的存在而蜿蜒向东北偏北方向漂移<ref name="prelim" /><ref name="TCD_10">{{cite web | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-10 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.010 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021101932/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.010 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="TCD_11">{{cite web | author = Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-11 | accessdate = 2008-07-14 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 11 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021101940/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.011 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.011 }}</ref>，并且在这一过程中也无法得以增强<ref name="TCD_12">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-11 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102444/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.012 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.012 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>。到了11月11日，一个低压槽令戈登以每小时13公里的速度向东北偏北移动<ref name="TCD_13">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-11 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 13 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021101952/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.013 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.013 }}</ref>，并且其风速也在经过加勒比海中部的过程中提高了9公里<ref name="TCD_14">{{cite web | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-11 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 14 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.014 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102037/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.014 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。低压槽继续令风暴转向，于11月12日下午转朝东面的牙买加逼近。虽然所经洋面水温较高，但戈登因受到强烈的上层对流层风切变的阻碍而无法增强<ref name="TCD_15">{{cite web | author = Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-12 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 15 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102119/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.015 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.015 }}</ref><ref name="TCD_16">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-12 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 16 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102124/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.016 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.016 }}</ref>，并且上层环流的组织性也受到打乱，风速降至每小时65公里<ref name="TCD_17">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-12 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.017 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102137/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.017 }}</ref>。

== 经过大安的列斯群岛 ==
[[Image:Gordon1994111400GOE7IR.jpg|thumb]]给[[海地|海地]]带去了大雨。]]
11月13日，佛罗里达南部以及墨西哥湾上空的低压槽继续令热带风暴戈登向东面的牙买加推进<ref name="TCD_18">{{cite web | author = Jarrell | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-12 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 18 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102219/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.018 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.018 }}</ref>，于黎明前在该岛东部边缘擦过<ref name="prelim" />，带去了189[[毫米|毫米]]降水<ref name="UWI_rainfall_Jam">{{cite web | author = Rafi Ahmad | publisher = Department of Geography and Geology, University of the West Indies, Mona, Kingston 7, Jamaica | title = GEOHAZ2001 page 016 | date = 2003-08-20 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | archivedate = 2012-02-13 | url = http://www.mona.uwi.edu/uds/GEOHAZARDS_2001/GEOHAZ2001-016.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120213165821/http://www.mona.uwi.edu/uds/GEOHAZARDS_2001/GEOHAZ2001-016.html }}</ref>。西南风向的风切变令风暴的风速没能超过每小时75公里，不过风切变和登陆都没有明显打乱气旋的组织结构<ref name="TCD_19">{{cite web | author = Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-13 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 19 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102718/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.019 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.019 }}</ref>。戈登接下来转向加速向东北行进<ref name="prelim" />，虽然风切变仍然阻止着热带气旋增强所需的上层发展，但风暴中还是有强劲的下层环流形成，虽然持续风速仍然只达到每小时65公里，但随着系统逼近[[古巴|古巴]]东部，当地报告出现了时速高速192公里的阵风<ref name="TCD_20">{{cite web | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-13 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102725/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.020 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.020 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>。风暴中心在[[关塔那摩湾|关塔那摩湾]]附近经过，同时风暴经过古巴东部期间给当地带去了暴雨<ref name="prelim" />，[[海地|海地]]西部的降水比古巴更多，营佩兰（{{lang|en|Camp-Perrin}}）报告的降雨量高达583毫米<ref>{{cite web | author = ORE | publisher = Organization for the Rehabilitation of the Environment | title = Rainfall — ORE — Camp-Perrin, Cayes, Haiti - 1994 | date = 1995-01-01 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | archivedate = 2012-02-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120212002113/http://oreworld.org/images/r_mm_eng/1994%20mm_eng.pdf | url = http://oreworld.org/images/r_mm_eng/1994%20mm_eng.pdf | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

与此同时，加勒比海大部分海域都由一片非常广阔的环流笼罩，热带风暴戈登只是其中的一部分，并且这片环流还在与[[佛罗里达海峡|佛罗里达海峡]]附近的一条上层对流层低压槽产生相互影响<ref name="TCD_21">{{cite web | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-13 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 21 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.021 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102734/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.021 }}</ref>。低压槽令大范围的上层气旋有所加强，还在加勒比海西部催生出另外几个下层环流，戈登也相应得以强化<ref name="prelim" />。戈登穿越古巴东部后，美国国家飓风中心相信风暴已在所有下层天气系统中占主导地位，并且已经吸收了这些系统的对流<ref name="prelim" />。不过，以[[气象学家|气象学家]]何塞·费尔南德斯-帕塔加斯（{{lang|en|Jose Fernandez-Partagas}}）为代表的少数意见认为，戈登的环流中心已经在古巴上空消散，位于巴哈马附近上空的低气压系统才是这时真正占主导地位的天气系统，这意味着热带风暴戈登已经消亡，该海域生成了一股新的热带风暴<ref>{{cite web | author = Jose Fernandez-Partagas | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1996-01-04 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Gordon: A Complex Weather System | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021114256/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/preloc/fern01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/preloc/fern01.gif }}</ref>。这一推断的可能性的确存在，但没有得到正式的飓风总结接受<ref name="prelim" /><ref name="Season_summary">{{cite journal | author = Avila, Lixion A. and Rappaport, Edward N. | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1996-01-04 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Atlantic Hurricane Season of 1994 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/mwr_pdf/1994.pdf | format = pdf | journal = Monthly Weather Review | volume = 124 | issue = 7 | pages = 1558–1578 | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1996)124<1558:AHSO>2.0.CO;2 | issn = 1520-0493 | archive-date = 2013-12-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131215203252/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/mwr_pdf/1994.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。到了11月13日夜幕降临时，戈登不但已经有过先后两次登陆，并且分别与三个竞争性的天气系统相互作用后继续保持存在，而且还在吸收巴哈马附近低气压的过程中获得[[冷心低压|冷心]]这一亚热带气旋的典型特征<ref name="prelim" /><ref name="TCD_22">{{cite web | author = Lawrence | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-13 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 22 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102739/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.022 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.022 }}</ref>。

戈登的深层气旋引导风暴向西北偏西方向移动，于11月14日进入[[特克斯和凯科斯群岛|特克斯和凯科斯群岛]]和巴哈马以南海域<ref name="prelim" />。美国[[中大西洋各州|中大西洋各州]]海岸附近上空的一片大型[[高气压|高压]][[高压脊|脊]]加大了风暴周围的[[气压梯度|气压梯度]]，因此系统的亚热带性质虽然令风暴缺少深层对流，其核心周围也不可能存在强风中心，但风暴的环流中心以外还是有强烈的风力存在。这些风的速度小幅上升到每小时85公里，但没能得到任何进一步增强<ref name="TCD_23">{{cite web | author = Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-14 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 23 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102749/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.023 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.023 }}</ref>。混合有热带气旋和亚热带气旋的戈登在高压脊的影响下继续向西北偏西行进并穿过巴哈马西部<ref name="prelim" /><ref name="TCD_24">{{cite web | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-14 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 24 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102822/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.024 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.024 }}</ref><ref name="TCD_25">{{cite web | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-14 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 25 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021102833/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.025 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.025 }}</ref>。这也令风暴的南部环流进入古巴西部上空，而一边增强的北部环流则在[[西棕榈滩|棕榈滩]]附近产生了时速90公里的大风<ref name="TCD_26">{{cite web | author = Rappaport/Jarrell | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-14 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 26 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021112441/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.026 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.026 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。11月15日，戈登途经佛罗里达礁岛群时在佛罗里达州的[[基韦斯特岛|基韦斯特岛]]实现了第四次登陆<ref name="prelim" />，然后继续向西经过群岛进入佛罗里达海峡，并且风暴的中心也开始回暖<ref name="TCD_27">{{cite web | author = Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-15 | accessdate = 2008-07-15 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.027 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021112508/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.027 }}</ref>，很快，深层对流的出现标志着戈登重新成为纯粹的热带气旋<ref name="TCD_28">{{cite web | author = Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-15 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 28 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021112935/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.028 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.028 }}</ref>。

== 在佛罗里达州的第二次登陆以及达到最高强度 ==
[[Image:Hurricane_Gordon_1994_nov_18_1308Z.jpg|thumb]]
影响风暴行动方向的转向气流仍然很弱<ref name="TCD_29">{{cite web | author = Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-15 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 29 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.029 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021112946/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.029 }}</ref><ref name="TCD_31">{{cite web | author = Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-16 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 31 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021112956/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.031 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.031 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>，让风暴在海上基本停止前进，并借此机会对深层对流进行全面的重新发展<ref name="prelim" /><ref name="TCD_31"/><ref name="TCD_30">{{cite web | author = Rappaport | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-15 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 30 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113013/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.030 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.030 }}</ref>。热带风暴戈登还在这一期间开始催生出多场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]。由于风暴中心仍然远离陆地，所以很可能有多个其产生的龙卷风未经报告，但佛罗里达海岸上还是有六场龙卷风着陆，其中四个达到[[藤田级数|藤田级数]]下的{{lang|en|F0}}级，有两个达到{{lang|en|F1}}级，还有一个估计风速高达每小时181至253公里，达到{{lang|en|F2}}级<ref name="FL_tornadoes">{{cite web | author = Staff Writers | publisher = 2008 Governor's Hurricane Conference | title = Infamous Florida Hurricanes | date = 2008-05-11 | accessdate = 2009-03-26 | url = http://www.flghc.org/ppt/WSG104-1994Gordon.pdf | format = pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090326075540/http://www.flghc.org/ppt/WSG104-1994Gordon.pdf | archivedate = 2009-03-26 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

在近海停留了近一天后，美国中部上空的一片中到上层对流层低压槽令热带风暴戈登开始北上，然后小幅转向东北偏北朝佛罗里达西海岸逼近<ref name="prelim" />，以每小时85公里风速在[[麦尔兹堡|麦尔兹堡]]和[[那不勒斯_(佛罗里达州)|那不勒斯]]之间登陆<ref name="TCD_32">{{cite web | author = Lawrence | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-16 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 32 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.032 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113056/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.032 }}</ref>。风暴东部的移动速度有所加快，戈登以每小时17公里的速度向佛罗里达半岛的东北方向行进<ref name="TCD_33">{{cite web | author = Lawrence | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-16 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 33 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113117/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.033 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.033 }}</ref>。风暴只花了六个小时就穿过半岛，并且强度几乎没有减弱，风速仍然保持在每小时85公里<ref name="TCD_33" />，其前进的速度也在继续加快<ref name="TCD_34">{{cite web | author = Rappaport | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-16 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 34 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.034 | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020122223/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.034 }}</ref>。11月17日清晨，回到开放海域的风暴中心气压开始降低<ref name="TCD_35">{{cite web | author = Rappaport | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-17 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 35 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113130/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.035 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.035 }}</ref>。11月17日，戈登突然催生出时速120公里的大风并由美国国家飓风中心升级为一级飓风<ref name="TCD_37">{{cite web | author = Lawrence | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-17 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Hurricane Gordon Special Discussion Number 37 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020122237/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.037 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.037 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-20 }}</ref>。不过系统组织上的改善并不明显<ref name="TCD_35" />，风切变也令中心和深层对流间的距离拉长<ref name="TCD_36">{{cite web | author = Lawrence | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-17 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 36 | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020122230/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.036 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.036 }}</ref>。

== 在佛罗里达州的第三次登陆和消亡 ==
引导戈登穿越佛罗里达州的短波槽移动到了风暴前方，[[美国东部|美国东部]]上空的一片[[高压脊|中层对流层高压脊]]开始对系统产生影响<ref name="prelim" />，风暴因此开始加速向东北方向移动，速度达到每小时40公里<ref name="TCD_38">{{cite web | author = Lawrence | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-17 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Hurricane Gordon Discussion Number 38 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113140/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.038 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.038 }}</ref>，到了11月17日晚又转向北上<ref name="prelim" /><ref name="TCD_39">{{cite web | author = Rappaport | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-17 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Hurricane Gordon Discussion Number 39 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.039 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113148/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.039 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref><ref name="TCD_40">{{cite web | author = Rappaport | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-18 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Hurricane Gordon Discussion Number 40 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020122242/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.040 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.040 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-20 }}</ref>。飓风继续以环状路径移动，并且在向西北偏西方向行进的过程中一度短暂威胁到北卡罗莱纳州的[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]<ref name="TCD_41">{{cite web | author = Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-18 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Hurricane Gordon Discussion Number 41 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113155/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.041 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.041 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>，然后又一次在海上基本停止前进<ref name="TCD_42">{{cite web | author = Rappaport | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-18 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Hurricane Gordon Discussion Number 42 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.042 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113220/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.042 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>。由于再度出现弱转向气流，戈登的强度有所削弱，回落为风速每小时110公里的热带风暴<ref name="prelim" /><ref name="TCD_43">{{cite web | author = Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-18 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 43 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113255/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.043 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.043 }}</ref>。11月18日，风暴在距外滩群岛仅150公里洋面开始转向南下远离北卡罗莱纳州海岸<ref name="TCD_44">{{cite web | author = Lawrence | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-18 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 44 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113313/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.044 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.044 }}</ref>。戈登掠过中大西洋各州，带去了50至130毫米降雨，其中最高的是[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]的[[诺福克郡|诺福克郡]]，达到133毫米<ref name="Mid Atl">{{cite book | author = Roth, David M | author2 = Weather Prediction Center | year = 2012 | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Point Maxima | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall in the Mid-Atlantic United States | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140203053004/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmidatl.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmidatl.html | archivedate = 2014-02-03 }}</ref>。温暖的[[海面温度|海面温度]]令系统的组织性得到改善<ref name="TCD_45">{{cite web | author = Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-19 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 45 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113438/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.045 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.045 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>，但风速却并未因此加快<ref name="TCD_46">{{cite web | author = Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-19 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 46 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.046 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113459/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.046 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>，风暴也在继续减弱。戈登受到来自西北方向的强烈上层风吹袭，其上层对流被切断，同时还因干冷空气的不利影响而导致下层对流也有所减弱<ref name="TCD_47">{{cite web | author = Mayfield, Max B | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-19 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 47 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113512/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.047 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.047 }}</ref>。

美国中部的一片高压系统向东飘移，令正在南下的戈登开始朝西转向<ref name="TCD_46" />，再度逼近西南方向的佛罗里达州<ref name="TCD_48">{{cite web | author = Lawrence | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-19 | accessdate = 2014-03-27 | title = Tropical Storm Gordon Discussion Number 48 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113527/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.048 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.048 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。由于缺乏深层对流，并且一直有着风切变的不利影响，戈登的风速终于降至低于热带风暴标准，于11月20日早上降级成热带低气压<ref name="TCD_49">{{cite web | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-20 | accessdate = 2014-03-27 | title = Tropical Depression Gordon Discussion Number 49 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.049 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113550/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.049 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>。陆地上空的高压系统继续令低气压向西推进<ref name="TCD_50">{{cite web | author = Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-20 | accessdate = 2014-03-27 | title = Tropical Depression Gordon Discussion Number 50 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113748/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.050 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.050 }}</ref><ref name="TCD_51">{{cite web | author = Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-20 | accessdate = 2014-03-27 | title = Tropical Depression Gordon Discussion Number 51 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113755/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.051 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.051 }}</ref>，直至当晚以每小时45公里风速在[[卡纳维拉尔角|卡纳维拉尔角]]附近进行了最后一次登陆<ref name="TCD_52">{{cite web | author = Lawrence | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-20 | accessdate = 2014-03-27 | title = Tropical Depression Gordon Discussion Number 52 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113805/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.052 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.052 }}</ref>。这场风暴在佛罗里达州的先后三次登陆共计给该州带去了130到250毫米降水，其中一个位于[[迈阿密-戴德县|迈阿密-戴德县]]库珀斯敦（{{lang|en|Cooperstown}}）的气象站记录到了高达409毫米的降雨量<ref name="HPC_Florida">{{cite web | author = Various Authors | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | date = 1995-01-01 | accessdate = 2008-07-16 | title = Subtropical Storm/Hurricane Gordon — November 11–22, 1994 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/gordon1994.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921105556/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/gordon1994.html | archivedate = 2013-09-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。风暴北上穿越佛罗里达州<ref name="TCD_53">{{cite web | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-21 | accessdate = 2014-03-27 | title = Tropical Depression Gordon Discussion Number 53 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.053 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113817/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.053 }}</ref><ref name="TCD_54">{{cite web | author = Jarrell | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1994-11-21 | accessdate = 2014-03-26 | title = Tropical Depression Gordon Discussion Number 54 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021113837/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.054 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/tropdisc/nal1294.054 | archivedate = 2012-10-21 }}</ref>，再向东北方向经过[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]，最终与[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]的一股锋面系统合并<ref name="prelim" /><ref name="TCD_54"/>。

=== 轨迹和预测 ===
戈登的行动轨迹与[[1972年大西洋飓风季#飓风唐恩|1972年的飓风唐恩]]（{{lang|en|Dawn}}）颇有几分类似<ref name="bs1119">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Baltimore Sun | date = 1994-11-19 | title = Gordon Batters N.C., Turns Back on Florida | accessdate = 2014-03-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/news/bs1119p3.gif | format = GIF | archivedate = 2014-03-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140327014707/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/news/bs1119p3.gif }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Baltimore Sun | date = 1994-11-19 | title = Gordon: Storm Heads Back to Florida | accessdate = 2014-03-27 | archivedate = 2014-03-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140327014913/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/news/bs1119p4.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1994/gordon/news/bs1119p4.gif | format = GIF }}</ref>。美国国家飓风中心称这股风暴是“一个复杂的（天气）系统，以不同寻常、飘忽不定的路径经过了西加勒比海及岛屿，佛罗里达州以及大西洋西南部”。由于其行进轨迹千回百转，该部门难以对戈登作出准确预测，出现错误的几率与之前的十年相比要高10到30个百分点<ref name="prelim" />。

